{"tid":673851,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"講出你食過 好與壞既米芝連食店","createTime":"2018-05-22T07:52:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T18:03:23.000Z","uid":106042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca16f94cd40388027425b6655d325a554debe906","tid":673851,"uid":106042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:52:42.000Z","msg":"好<br />\n<br />\n合益泰 <br />\n依家尚算平民 腸粉加芝麻正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n壞<br />\n<br />\n元朗 好到底麵家 <br />\n細細碗 蝦子雲吞 普通但貴<br />\n<br />\n荃灣 新斗記<br />\n叫左半圍菜 order完5分鐘竟然可以上到菜<br />\n乳豬係涼既 應該係切定 <br />\n一定點醬加沙糖先好味<br />\n<br />\n其他7道菜冇水準<br />\n埋單3千幾 失望而回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db075c47004fef27cdf737923ef7f0656919ac55","tid":673851,"uid":109224,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T17:13:15.000Z","msg":"好:龍吟，Amber <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心機之作<br />\n壞: 鼎泰豐，狗仔粉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母"},{"pid":"04ccafed6938c114adeaf01abde78baeb3d28bbf","tid":673851,"uid":9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T17:14:59.000Z","msg":"好:西環 嘗囍,食點心<br />\n拎米芝蓮之前好惦,拎左之後食唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566d561b0e6d0ab2c6493ab67b7075a5dc11ed2c","tid":673851,"uid":187938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db075c47004fef27cdf737923ef7f0656919ac55","tid":673851,"uid":109224,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T17:13:15.000Z","msg":"好:龍吟，Amber <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心機之作<br />\n壞: 鼎泰豐，狗仔粉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T17:25:41.000Z","msg":"想知巴打龍吟係幾時去食，有咩咁特別？"},{"pid":"99c015e24ee1220aef843a3f62f62a27c7c724ba","tid":673851,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"